title: Ocracoke_Observer
exrest: The Ocracoke Observer is a print and online newspaper produced in Ocracoke, NC. The paper is created on Ocracoke and printed in Greenville, NC. Ten print issues are produced every year and news is posted on a daily basis on the Ocracoke Observer website. Circulation of the print edition fluctuates seasonally and ranges from 2,500 to 6,000.
